This project re-implements, as lean original code, several design *patterns*
studied from the following MIT-licensed project (no source copied verbatim):

  @yemi33/minions — https://github.com/yemi33/minions (MIT)
    - git worktree isolation + pool + garbage collection
    - per-provider permission/flag table (Claude / Copilot / Codex)
    - headless handling of the MCP "trust this server?" prompt
    - cron-style scheduler with schedule-time template variables
    - preflight / timeout / watchdog / cooldown safety patterns

See DESIGN.md §20 for details.
